text: Friedrich Schwarz (born 1880, date of death unknown) was a German fencer. He competed in the individual and team épée and sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:Year of death missing Category:German male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Germany Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mainz
